message.raw:
- In andor_capabilities.py, removed an indent on class set_
functions
- In andor_solis.py added GetNumberVSSpeeds and  GetVSSpeed
funcs
- In andor_utils.py, further tested FK modes with multiple
acquisitions. For some reason the GetReadoutTime() call
breaks the test, have to investigate this later. The names
snap() and grab_acquisition() have changed for acquire() and
download_acquisition for the sake of clarity.
- In blacks_workers.py, changes in grab_multiple to
do most of the sequence acquisitions.
